#### 2. No Rate Limiting — Denial of Service / Brute Force (OWASP A05)

All endpoints are completely unthrottled. An attacker can hammer the server freely.

**Fix:**
```js
const rateLimit = require('express-rate-limit');

const limiter = rateLimit({
