| 3 | 🟠 Medium | A05 Security Misconfiguration | No security headers (helmet) |
| 4 | 🟠 Medium | A05 Security Misconfiguration | No CORS policy defined |
| 5 | 🟠 Medium | A07 Identification & Auth | No rate limiting |
| 6 | 🟡 Low | A04 Insecure Design | PII (email) exposed without authorization |
| 7 | 🟡 Low | A09 Logging & Monitoring | No request logging or error handling |
| 8 | 🟡 Low | A05 Security Misconfiguration | Server port hardcoded, not configurable |

